### 电影日记 API 测试

# 基础 URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/movie-diary
@authUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/auth

# 用户认证（先执行这个获取 userId）
# @userId 从响应中复制

### 用户注册
POST {{authUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户"
}

### 用户登录
POST {{authUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 获取当前用户信息
GET {{authUrl}}/me
X-User-Id: 1

### ====================================

### 1. 创建电影日记
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "tmdbMovieId": 550,
  "movieTitle": "搏击俱乐部",
  "watchDate": "2026-03-13",
  "rating": 9.0,
  "review": "非常经典的电影，剧情反转令人震撼！",
  "posterUrl": "https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/poster.jpg",
  "isFavorite": true
}

### 2. 查询所有电影日记（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}?page=1&size=10
X-User-Id: 1

### 3. 根据 ID 查询电影日记
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
X-User-Id: 1

### 4. 更新电影日记
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "movieTitle": "搏击俱乐部",
  "watchDate": "2026-03-13",
  "rating": 9.5,
  "review": "再次观看，依然震撼！剧情设计太精妙了。",
  "posterUrl": "https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/poster.jpg",
  "isFavorite": true
}

### 5. 删除电影日记
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
X-User-Id: 1

### 6. 根据 TMDB 电影 ID 查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/tmdb/550
X-User-Id: 1

### 7. 根据日期范围查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/date-range?startDate=2026-03-01&endDate=2026-03-31
X-User-Id: 1

### 8. 查询收藏的电影日记
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites
X-User-Id: 1

### 9. 统计电影总数
GET {{baseUrl}}/count
X-User-Id: 1
